Changed the drums - Verse/Intro lick was not quite correct.

The last phrase BD's are not all in the song, but as mentioned previously, they sound good so they were kept.

Apparently, the song is actually 90 BPM, but this version is subdivided into eighth notes instead of 16ths (no reason to change)

NOTE: This is not EXACTLY the same as the song. It will play along to the song but it is not EXACTLY the same. If you want it to be exactly the same, then use this as a template and make your own version (just print, no need to revise).
